project_descr: This project will finalize the MDG Acceleration Framework (MAF) in Grenada via the development of an MDG Acceleration country action Plan (MAP).

outputs.output_descr: The initiative aims to localize MDGs in Grenada. Results of the project include a prioritization of targets, action, indicators for Grenada and the integration of MDGs in National Planning and budget frameworks.
outputs.crs_descr: Public sector policy and administrative management
